title: 11YA: The Ladies' Championship
body_text:
The last few calendars have been very special for ECD.
At the 3YA, John Tronolone went face-to-face with fellow ECD#1 combatant Jim Butler. Winston sisters Valerie and Lauren competed at the 1YA and reprised their roles at the 5th birthday in 2010. In 2012, ECD members returned to the hallowed grounds of Ocean Road Park while last year's "Decade of Dodgeball" revived major rivalries of the past in a match featuring Megill, Pierce, Edwards, and Tom.
Now it's 2016 - some 132 months - and I couldn't be more proud to announce the following encounter. And like the 11YA, you will never see it again.
